oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Benton County Courthouse, Camden, Tenn.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color photograph of the exterior of the Benton County Courthouse. There are cars in the street and parked in front of the courthouse. Features a white border, divided back, and narrative on reverse. "Benton" is written in green marker in the correspondence area. Note: this is an additional copy of this postcard and is the same as 49121. [No. S-41752-1]
